history.content:
"Applications will be processed on a rolling basis in 2-week cycles. That means every two weeks we will review our new applicants. Then you will either be added to the class, or put on the waiting list. You will be notified of updates via email. The first cycle will be on Sunday, May 13. If you submit your application before then, you will be included in the first cycle."

They haven't processed the first cycle of applications yet.
I remember I submitted a interest-form-like document and then never heard any information about it. May I ask for some updates? Thanks!
